name: Init.css
tagline: The perfect style for your project or reading pages
body:
# init.css
### @auhtor : @lukyvj

A css stylesheet that needs less HTML structure, for better result .

##Description
  With init.css, you only focus on inline tags. No need to add divs, or any bloc elements. 
  If you want a kind of gihub pages site for a project and you only want to write the text.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
